# Memory IC Resources

This folder contains books, courses, tutorials, and papers for learning memory IC design.

## Books
- *Digital Integrated Circuits* – Jan M. Rabaey
- *CMOS VLSI Design* – Weste & Harris
- *Design of Analog CMOS Integrated Circuits* – Behzad Razavi

## Online Courses
- NPTEL: Digital & Analog VLSI Design
- Coursera / Udemy: Verilog / SystemVerilog
- Cadence tutorials: Virtuoso, SPICE simulation

## Tutorials
- HSPICE / Spectre simulation guides
- Python/TCL automation for IC design

## Research Papers
- IEEE Transactions on VLSI
- ISSCC / IEDM memory design papers
